@startuml activity_place_overseas_orders
title Activity Diagram - PlaceOverseasOrders

start
:International Ordering Department triggers order generation;
:System retrieves active Allocation Plan;
:Group allocation lines by Import Site;
:For each Site, compose an Overseas Order;
:Specify delivery means (ship delivery / air delivery);
:Transmit official orders to selected Sites;
:Overseas Import Sites receive and process orders;
:Sites send Acknowledgements back to the system;
:System updates Order status to Transmitted;
stop
@enduml
